# {{ .ProviderShortName | title }} Provider

The {{ .ProviderShortName | title }} provider is used to manage resources in the SELECT data platform. SELECT helps organizations optimize their Snowflake costs by providing usage group management and cost allocation capabilities.

## About Select

[Select](https://select.dev) helps organizations optimize their Snowflake usage and costs. This Terraform provider enables Infrastructure as Code management of Select platform resources like usage groups and usage group sets.



